,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:32:33.000Z","msg":"你地講到比人告個班mk冇請辯護律師咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c51c1599cd53bc99acd1ec0f35a611b8c170acf","tid":485732,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚鬼知咩<br />\n個官問d野好似審緊個毒撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係，明明係條仔比人打<br />\n<br />\n依家審到好似佢抵比人打咁"},{"pid":"22ab5587ecdc3174ccb8fdd75a610883db648978","tid":485732,"uid":86587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，做毒撚做到咁嘅樣真係抵比人打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0882657b2452358c0a2ef0db96d417b4d63b0d7a","tid":485732,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實單案係點<br />\n打人班人比人告<br />\n定個毒撚比人告？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打人果班俾人告, 毒撚係證人.<br />\n<br />\n法庭上嘅供詞, 如果證明證人有違法行為, 法庭可以指令執法部門跟進, 而法庭通常都想避免有咁嘅事發生, 所以有責任提提證人小心作供."},{"pid":"9b757c13dfb2f9814f20142f2defafa79c6cb46a","tid":485732,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇野，咁點解比人打完又比人告返轉頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇比人告返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n係啲戇鳩媒體寫到受害人好似係被告咁樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c363469baf4ba939f85400f64c233540b0f95e4","tid":485732,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>羅進一步表示，有些女孩會稱呼他作「狗公」，令他感到嬲怒，因此才會說出侮辱說話。羅揚言自己沒有做錯，他只是想識女友，「做乜要放我高登&hellip;&hellip;吖，唔係&hellip;&hellip;係Facebook」。他又謂：「我有咩唔好？我有咩問題？做咩話性格不合？」<br />\n<br />\n律師根據一些網上截圖，問羅為何很多時劈頭第一句便問人「扑唔扑嘢」。羅急急澄清自己只是「口快快」，其實他有「深層意思」，只因自己讀不成書，文法不好，加上他當時情緒不穩，在男女關係中「屢戰屢敗」，所以說話會「直接啲」。法官聞言問：「呢個就係你深層意思？」羅答：「其實有更深層意思。」隨後強調當天只想「談戀愛」，即「行街睇戲食飯嗰類囉」。</blockquote><br />\n好似上進養0lai</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80aa14975fbf34d9f008f4118cf3132351cb55eb","tid":485732,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線快過我出POST，仲諗住出POST屌毒撚同cosplayer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e69e58201a91a0153bbcd2e5733a936537ddf6e","tid":485732,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線快過我出POST，仲諗住出POST屌毒撚同cosplayer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持"},{"pid":"98f37fc6e4e90add72150a558cf5f1adcf849cd0","tid":485732,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線快過我出POST，仲諗住出POST屌毒撚同cosplayer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持</blockquote><br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d979f296e694625de95c229ec05815451e710ea","tid":485732,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線快過我出POST，仲諗住出POST屌毒撚同cosplayer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持</blockquote><br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nG持"},{"pid":"07834c33a789fc5e5b90228c59e5af39beb8b24c","tid":485732,"uid":87132,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:25:48.000Z","msg":"就算審完條友係犯賤<b